---
title: Spiced Chicken & Red Wine Onion Sauce with Cheesy Fries & Celery Slaw
description: A fantastic sauce can transform any dinner from rags to riches. This All-American chicken is getting a fairytale makeover with a decadent red wine and caramelised onion sauce. The transformation is complete, now dig in and enjoy the magic!
We’ve replaced the
pea pods in this recipe
with carrot due to local
ingredient availability.
It’ll be just as delicious,
just follow your recipe
card!
